re_item_assets/steam/apps/1870330/extras/21bf7a1b4825be523ab631e6ecdd95ae.webm?t=1667943559\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1870330/extras/21bf7a1b4825be523ab631e6ecdd95ae.mp4?t=1667943559\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>Gigmaker allows you to make your own gigs from scratch and share it with your friends. <br>Create lasting memories with memorable lighting and music. <br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1870330/extras/2d0a48054e3b1685e9d6bcb51418e333.poster.avif?t=1667943559\" width=600 height=250 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1870330/extras/2d0a48054e3b1685e9d6bcb51418e333.webm?t=1667943559\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1870330/extras/2d0a48054e3b1685e9d6bcb51418e333.mp4?t=1667943559\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>",
